questions.question:
What will be rendered by the following code?

```jsx
function Greeting({ name }) {
  return <h1>Hello, {name}</h1>;
}

<Greeting name="React" />
```

What will the following code output?

```jsx
function Card({ children }) {
  return <div className="card">{children}</div>;
}

<Card>
  <h1>Title</h1>
</Card>
```

What will the following code output if no `name` prop is passed?

```jsx
function Hello({ name }) {
  return <div>Hello {name}</div>;
}

<Hello />
```

What will the following code output?

```jsx
function List({ items }) {
  return <ul>{items}</ul>;
}

<List items={['a', 'b']} />
```
